Discription: Mirror Fold
Features: 1. Plug and Play no cutting of wires required. 2. Activate the feature of automatic side mirror Fold and Unfold with Car Central Locking Remote. 3. It must require that car have button inside to operate function of mirror fold and unfold. 4. There are 2 options in Interface. A) Option 1: Mirror Fold when lock the Car and Unfold when give Ignition to car not on Unlock because it save Motor cycle of the Mirror by unnecessary fold and Unfold of mirror on Lock and Unlock as we not always unlock car for drive the car. B) Option 2: Mirror Fold on Lock and Unfold on Unlock the Car. (Interface is programmed with Option: 1 and if need to switch Option: 2 just cut 1 interlink in wiring harness. 5. Advantage is if Mirror is Fold it ensures that Car is locked.
